file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description: '<font size="2" color="red">MIT License</font>'
  title: "Open-Street-Maps"
  contact:
    name: Erlan Lucio
    url: https://github.com/lucioerlan
  version: '1.0'
servers:
- url: http://localhost:5000/api
  variables: {}
paths:
  /get-all-mapa:
    get:
      tags:
      - ROUTES
      summary: GET ALL MAPA
      operationId: GETALLMAPA
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
  /getid-mapa:
    get:
      tags:
      - ROUTES
      summary: GET ID MAPA
      operationId: GETIDMAPA
      parameters:
      - name: id
        in: query
        description: ''
        required: true
        style: form
        explode: true
        schema:
          type: string
          example: 60978a7679b72839d8f8f4eb
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
  /store-mapa:
    post:
      tags:
      - ROUTES
      summary: STORE MAPA
      operationId: STOREMAPA
      parameters: []
      requestBody:
        description: ''
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/STOREMAPAREQUEST'
            example:
              tracking: '553366'
              lat: '10.74044'
              lon: '-74.755272'
              plate: WBAPM73589A254790
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
  /update-mapa:
    put:
      tags:
      - ROUTES
      summary: UPDATE MAPA
      operationId: UPDATEMAPA
      parameters: []
      requestBody:
        description: ''
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/UPDATEMAPAREQUEST'
            example:
              id: 60978a7679b72839d8f8f4eb
              tracking: '553366'
              lat: '10.74045'
              lon: '-74.755278'
              plate: WBAP1
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
components:
  schemas:
    STOREMAPAREQUEST:
      title: STOREMAPAREQUEST
      required:
      - tracking
      - lat
      - lon
      - plate
      type: object
      properties:
        tracking:
          type: string
        lat:
          type: string
        lon:
          type: string
        plate:
          type: string
      example:
        tracking: '553366'
        lat: '10.74044'
        lon: '-74.755272'
        plate: WBAPM73589A254790
    UPDATEMAPAREQUEST:
      title: UPDATEMAPAREQUEST
      required:
      - id
      - tracking
      - lat
      - lon
      - plate
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        tracking:
          type: string
        lat:
          type: string
        lon:
          type: string
        plate:
          type: string
      example:
        id: 60978a7679b72839d8f8f4eb
        tracking: '553366'
        lat: '10.74045'
        lon: '-74.755278'
        plate: WBAP1
tags:
- name: ROUTES
